Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:10.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:38.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yami face off with the leader \Nof the Eye of the Midnight Sun, Licht,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and end up in a life or death situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:43.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.35,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Ray of Divine Punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He came.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.32,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But at that moment, Finral and Gauche arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.28,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.45,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Full Reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:02.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche used a miraculous spell, and Licht's \Nown spell was reflected right back at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:04.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how big it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirrors reflect light!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:07.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Though just barely,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:11.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they were finally able to defeat the leader \Nof the Eye of the Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.77,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Three Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That was really something, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:03.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral! Gauche! What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's the speed of light. There's \Nno way he could've dodged all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:17.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you came back, Gauche! \NWay to steal all the glory, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:23.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here because you picked \Nme up that one day, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:28.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So I guess it's basically my glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:33.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami, you didn't even do \Nanything! Gauche did all the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:40.78,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurts, Captain Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:40.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky just because \Nyou beat the scrawny dude, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Captain Yami, Gauche, \NAsta, we all worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.04,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.04,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,None of this would've happened \Nwithout my spatial magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get me back to Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I have seniority over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.64,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Marie... Your big brother did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'll hug me and \Ntell me how great I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait! Ah, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I'm your senior...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:12.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And I told you I could only \Nuse my magic one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I have to recover my \Nmagic first. Just wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.93,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really just do that?! \NYou, too, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make Marie wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... You're so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.78,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like his own ultimate \Nspell did a number on him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:38.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he had another archenemy \Nbesides me. Don't worry 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,risk hurting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? You know him? \NSorry I beat the crap out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.02,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't know this bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.74,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't get it at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but we're going to take you back \Nto Magic Knights Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You'll spill everything there is to know\Nabout the Eye of the Midnight Sun there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Hot-Blooded King of \NHardnoses has been avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,May he rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, quit sweatin' the minor details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Minor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:30.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Let's see, Dark Binding Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when are those \Nreinforcements getting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:53.54,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Black Bulls girl, I already \Ncontacted your captain quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.94,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,And what a bah-hassle it was.\NHe wouldn't listen to a word I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So where's Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.02,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,He should've left a while bah-hack. Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:07.76,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.01,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca, Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:22.29,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha... My shift's about over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.17,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll head home and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.65,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my captain's awake yet. \NGuess I should report this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:33.57,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,"Why didn't you report this to me? \NDo you want to get sliced in half? Skree!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:35.85,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I definitely don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.62,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:39.89,main,Kid a,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.63,main,Parents,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.64,main,Kid b,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.52,main,Kid b mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt? Do you feel okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.88,main,Kid B,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.88,main,Kid c Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The kids from the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.14,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,They're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.09,main,Kid b,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights came to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.90,main,Kid b mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! We owe you everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, we just fulfilled our \Nduty as Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.43,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, all I did was contact them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.62,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But why did he go straight over \Nthere without stopping here first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I got left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:22.07,main,Kid A,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Theresa also used these \Namazing spells and saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:26.17,main,Kid c,0000,0000,0000,,There was a really scary man. \NHe was covered in mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.03,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Luca and Marco? They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Gauche... Say, what \Nhappened to the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.23,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca! Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.61,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.52,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.98,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.62,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.87,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Theresa... A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:07.63,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me. I've still \Ngot at least a hundred years to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:11.63,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for saving these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.76,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just me. Those brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.56,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, please don't talk any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That robe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:26.05,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Asta lent it to me. He said I \Nwouldn't be scared if I wore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:30.48,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,And he was right! I felt so\Nmuch braver. I didn't cry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.73,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where's Asta? What happened to Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.73,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.45,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Well... The battle's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.57,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.75,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.42,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun.\NHe called himself Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So Asta's fighting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.52,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Along with some captain named Yami and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:59.43,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,My brother went to help them, along \Nwith someone who uses spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.18,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everything will be okay!\NI believe in my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right. Everything will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:10.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They won't lose. I'm sure \Nthey'll come back victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.96,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Finral and Gauche
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.70,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,should've taken me with them if they \Ncame all the way back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:22.58,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it! It's not \Nthat I'm worried about Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.96,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights! It's because \NI'm one of the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:30.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez. Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:36.80,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, well.. It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:59.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I used a lot of magic. It's not \Ngoing to recover that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.41,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, tch, tch, tch! Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.61,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making Marie wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:11.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any extra magic, unlike you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:16.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on... The longer we wait,\Nthe happier she might be to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wouldn't mind that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't mind what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.83,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you a single thing about Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who gets close to Marie is my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least bring me some \Nbreakfast with your spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.87,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a delivery service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:39.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But that guy's passed out... So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.30,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this definitely doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.57,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Licht and Val \Nare in a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.63,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm usually pretty lazy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.31,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta save my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.36,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a unique design.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.53,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it really matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.49,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! He can move at light speed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:05.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:10.08,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Man, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:14.71,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,But this should be easy to fix, so whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.88,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Healing Light Particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That magic... It's the \Nsame as Round Eyebrows's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.38,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You came...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:28.22,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. My strength alone wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.72,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Licht, does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, now that you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.13,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:43.30,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Phoenix Robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.67,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to worry about,\Nnow that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.54,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.88,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht... It's a pain in the butt if you \Ntry to shoulder everything yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:10.58,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insects do \Nthat to my comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.99,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:16.90,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stomp you like ants and rip you apart, \Nlike I'm ripping the wings off a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:21.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate those who have hurt Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.46,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.41,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They are the strongest three \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:39.29,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In combat, they surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.30,sign_19644_200_Third_Eye,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Third Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.48,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're more powerful than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Third Eye, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.10,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be bluffing when he says \Nthey're stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.10,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much trouble to bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:02.86,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the name suggests, your kingdom\Ntakes the clover as its symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:09.72,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Within the clover's leaves are \Npleasant words that do not suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.87,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Namely: faith, hope, and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:18.37,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I've given them names that \Nmean the opposite of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:24.38,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,With a name meaning the opposite\Nof faith, Raia the Disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:24.38,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,1)}Raia the Disloyal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:29.27,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,With a name meaning the opposite\Nof hope, Vetto the Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.89,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,1)}Vetto the Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:35.77,top,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,And with a name meaning the opposite\Nof love, Fana the Hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.77,sign_20632_210_Raia_the_Disloya,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(757,813)}Fana the Hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:40.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill those who have \Nhurt Licht. I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,"Disloyal," "Despair," and "Hateful."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those names sound grand and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but your names aren't enough \Nto tell us how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.65,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we'll just \Nhave to prove it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.23,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,even though it's a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Captain Yami's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.67,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Copy Magic: Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Raia the Disloyal, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go ripping off people's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sue you for copyright infringement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:17.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Bear Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.24,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. My magic hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.55,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid mosquitoes and dragonflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.37,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The jerk read my ki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:52.63,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Magic: Bear Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.02,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Let me see the despair \Nin your faces, little mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you taste best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:09.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! This katana was \Ncustom-made and crazy expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You better pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:16.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch... I haven't even finished \Npaying this thing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.97,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you... I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.29,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander... That must be spirit magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.84,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The same as... Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Fana the Hateful, was it? Nobody likes \Nhysterical chicks, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.78,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's not fully \Ndeveloped yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.77,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The fire spirit, one of \Nthe four great attributes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.57,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.03,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:02.33,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return Licht's pain \Nhundreds of times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.18,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.69,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Burn them to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.69,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you working hard? I wonder\Nhow long you can keep it up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.19,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.45,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. Because we're here, Yami is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:50.17,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't recovered enough \Nto use my spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.67,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're on a completely different level!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're thousands... No, a million \Nyears too early for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit tight and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me surpass my limits, \Nright here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, you won't go down easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.32,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:22.74,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Each of them is stronger \Nthan a Magic Knight Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.50,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time we end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.53,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.92,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Magic: Salamander's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.26,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.64,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.22,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Let us play, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:23.40,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger than a Magic Knight Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.18,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we test out that theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:31.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man... Another second or two, \Nand something would've awakened in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do about this,\Nyou lousy so-called friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:38.44,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can even say those \Nwords when you look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:43.99,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to execute you myself someday, \Nso be ready and wait, foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking.\NYou and your stupid haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.55,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, how pathetic are you that \Nyou actually have to rely on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, harsh as always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:57.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're Magic Knight Captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You need to show more interest \Nif you're a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.64,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I only care about Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you even know my name, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:16.40,sign_28996_297_Captain_of_the_P,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,769)}Captain of the Green Praying Mantises\N{\fs30}Jack the Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:15.03,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the Green Praying Mantises, \NJack the Ripper, who uses severing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.60,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's super sadistic, has a destruction fetish,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,and likes to brag whenever he \Ncuts anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:23.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he cut down a mountain \Nafter a squabble with Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:31.18,sign_28996_297_Captain_of_the_P,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,769)}Captain of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nozel Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:29.70,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The warhorse, the royal captain \Nof the Silver Eagles, Nozel Silva.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:34.12,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at his sparkly aura. \NMan, is he hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:34.92,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:42.67,sign_28996_297_Captain_of_the_P,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Blue Rose Knights\N{\fs30}Charlotte Roselei
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:41.61,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the Blue Rose Knights,\Nthe cool and beautiful Charlotte Roselei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're excited all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful! I want \Nto get closer to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.15,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So, three Magic Knight Captains...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:00.78,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. It doesn't matter how many people...\Nno, vermin show up. They're no match for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:05.24,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill those who \Nharm Licht... All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:10.07,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, let's get things started.\N I'll chop you all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.74,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.25,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:59.27,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.36,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:02.81,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}So Tired
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.53,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So Tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:08.36,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So tired. Spring is nice and warm, \Nand I can sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:16.77,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping on the beach \Nin summer is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:22.83,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn is for food, autumn is for art...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.65,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,And winter is for hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.72,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,He's just sleeping all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:35.70,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have trouble falling asleep, so I \Nhate everyone who can sleep so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.72,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Just wish these voices would shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.44,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired.
